#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn12.31"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.31:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.31:0.2"
msgid "4. Kaḷārakhattiyavagga "
msgstr "4. Kaḷāra the Aristocrat "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn12.31:0.3"
msgid "31. Bhūtasutta "
msgstr "31. What Has Come to Be "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn12.31:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.31:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to Venerable Sāriputta, "

#. VAR: pārāyane → pārāyaṇe (bj) | parāyane (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn12.31:1.3"
msgid "“vuttamidaṃ, sāriputta, pārāyane ajitapañhe: "
msgstr "“Sāriputta, this was said in ‘The Way to the Beyond’, in ‘The Questions of Ajita’: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn12.31:2.1"
msgid "‘Ye ca saṅkhātadhammāse, "
msgstr "‘Those who have comprehended the teaching, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:2.2"
msgid "ye ca sekkhā puthū idha; "
msgstr "and the many kinds of trainees here—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:2.3"
msgid "Tesaṃ me nipako iriyaṃ, "
msgstr "dear sir, you are alert; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:2.4"
msgid "puṭṭho pabrūhi mārisā’ti. "
msgstr "when questioned, please tell me their conduct.’ "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn12.31:3.1"
msgid "Imassa nu kho, sāriputta, saṅkhittena bhāsitassa kathaṃ vitthārena attho daṭṭhabbo”ti? "
msgstr "How should we see the detailed meaning of this brief statement?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.31:3.2"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā sāriputto tuṇhī ahosi. "
msgstr "When he said this, Sāriputta kept silent. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn12.31:4.1"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ āmantesi … pe … "
msgstr "For a second time … "

msgctxt "sn12.31:4.2"
msgid "dutiyampi kho āyasmā sāriputto tuṇhī ahosi. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.31:4.3"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ āmantesi: "
msgstr "For a third time … "

msgctxt "sn12.31:4.4"
msgid "“vuttamidaṃ, sāriputta, pārāyane ajitapañhe: "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn12.31:5.1"
msgid "‘Ye ca saṅkhātadhammāse, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:5.2"
msgid "ye ca sekkhā puthū idha; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:5.3"
msgid "Tesaṃ me nipako iriyaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:5.4"
msgid "puṭṭho pabrūhi mārisā’ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.48, sc6
msgctxt "sn12.31:6.1"
msgid "Imassa nu kho, sāriputta, saṅkhittena bhāsitassa kathaṃ vitthārena attho daṭṭhabbo”ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.31:6.2"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho āyasmā sāriputto tuṇhī ahosi. "
msgstr "Sāriputta kept silent. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn12.31:7.1"
msgid "“Bhūtamidanti, sāriputta, passasī”ti? "
msgstr "“Sāriputta, do you see that this has come to be?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.31:7.2"
msgid "“Bhūtamidanti, bhante, yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati. "
msgstr "“Sir, one truly sees with right wisdom that this has come to be. "

msgctxt "sn12.31:7.3"
msgid "Bhūtamidanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā bhūtassa nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti. "
msgstr "Seeing this, one is practicing for disillusionment, dispassion, and cessation regarding what has come to be. "

msgctxt "sn12.31:7.4"
msgid "Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati. "
msgstr "One truly sees with right wisdom that it originated with that as fuel. "

msgctxt "sn12.31:7.5"
msgid "Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā āhārasambhavassa nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti. "
msgstr "Seeing this, one is practicing for disillusionment, dispassion, and cessation regarding the fuel for its origination. "

msgctxt "sn12.31:7.6"
msgid "Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati. "
msgstr "One truly sees with right wisdom that when that fuel ceases, what has come to be is liable to cease. "

msgctxt "sn12.31:7.7"
msgid "Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā nirodhadhammassa nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti. "
msgstr "Seeing this, one is practicing for disillusionment, dispassion, and cessation regarding what is liable to cease. "

msgctxt "sn12.31:7.8"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhante, sekkho hoti. "
msgstr "In this way one is a trainee. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.49, sc8
msgctxt "sn12.31:8.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhante, saṅkhātadhammo hoti? "
msgstr "And what, sir, is one who has comprehended the teaching? "

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.2"
msgid "Bhūtamidanti, bhante, yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati. "
msgstr "Sir, one truly sees with right wisdom that this has come to be. "

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.3"
msgid "Bhūtamidanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā bhūtassa nibbidā virāgā nirodhā anupādā vimutto hoti. "
msgstr "Seeing this, one is freed by not grasping through disillusionment, dispassion, and cessation regarding what has come to be. "

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.4"
msgid "Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati. "
msgstr "One truly sees with right wisdom that it originated with that as fuel. "

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.5"
msgid "Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā āhārasambhavassa nibbidā virāgā nirodhā anupādā vimutto hoti. "
msgstr "Seeing this, one is freed by not grasping through disillusionment, dispassion, and cessation regarding the fuel for its origination. "

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.6"
msgid "Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati. "
msgstr "One truly sees with right wisdom that when that fuel ceases, what has come to be is liable to cease. "

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.7"
msgid "Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā nirodhadhammassa nibbidā virāgā nirodhā anupādā vimutto hoti. "
msgstr "Seeing this, one is freed by not grasping through disillusionment, dispassion, and cessation regarding what is liable to cease. "

msgctxt "sn12.31:8.8"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhante, saṅkhātadhammo hoti. "
msgstr "In this way one has comprehended the teaching. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.31:8.9"
msgid "Iti kho, bhante, yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ pārāyane ajitapañhe: "
msgstr "Sir, regarding what was said in ‘The Way to the Beyond’, in ‘The Questions of Ajita’: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "sn12.31:9.1"
msgid "‘Ye ca saṅkhātadhammāse, "
msgstr "‘Those who have comprehended the teaching, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:9.2"
msgid "ye ca sekkhā puthū idha; "
msgstr "and the many kinds of trainees here—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:9.3"
msgid "Tesaṃ me nipako iriyaṃ, "
msgstr "dear sir, you are alert; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:9.4"
msgid "puṭṭho pabrūhi mārisā’ti. "
msgstr "when questioned, please tell me their conduct.’ "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "sn12.31:10.1"
msgid "Imassa khvāhaṃ, bhante, saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāmī”ti. "
msgstr "This is how I understand the detailed meaning of what was said in brief.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "sn12.31:11.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, sāriputta, bhūtamidanti, sāriputta, yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati. "
msgstr "“Good, good, Sāriputta!” (The Buddha repeated all of Sāriputta’s explanation, concluding:) "

msgctxt "sn12.31:11.2"
msgid "Bhūtamidanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā bhūtassa nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.31:11.3"
msgid "Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.31:11.4"
msgid "Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā āhārasambhavassa nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.31:11.5"
msgid "Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.31:11.6"
msgid "Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā nirodhadhammassa nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya paṭipanno hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.31:11.7"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, sāriputta, sekkho hoti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.50, sc12
msgctxt "sn12.31:12.1"
msgid "Kathañca, sāriputta, saṅkhātadhammo hoti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.2"
msgid "Bhūtamidanti, sāriputta, yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.3"
msgid "Bhūtamidanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā bhūtassa nibbidā virāgā nirodhā anupādā vimutto hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.4"
msgid "Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.5"
msgid "Tadāhārasambhavanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā āhārasambhavassa nibbidā virāgā nirodhā anupādā vimutto hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.6"
msgid "Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.7"
msgid "Tadāhāranirodhā yaṃ bhūtaṃ taṃ nirodhadhammanti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññā disvā nirodhadhammassa nibbidā virāgā nirodhā anupādā vimutto hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.8"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, sāriputta, saṅkhātadhammo hoti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.31:12.9"
msgid "Iti kho, sāriputta, yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ pārāyane ajitapañhe: "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc13
msgctxt "sn12.31:13.1"
msgid "‘Ye ca saṅkhātadhammāse, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:13.2"
msgid "ye ca sekkhā puthū idha; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:13.3"
msgid "Tesaṃ me nipako iriyaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn12.31:13.4"
msgid "puṭṭho pabrūhi mārisā’ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc14
msgctxt "sn12.31:14.1"
msgid "Imassa kho, sāriputta, saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena attho daṭṭhabbo”ti. "
msgstr "This is how to understand the detailed meaning of what was said in brief.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.31:14.2"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

